---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';
import { approach, consultationHref, email, expectations, phoneDisplay, phoneHref } from '../data/site';
import '../styles/global.css';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const schema = { '@context':'https://schema.org','@type':'Person',name:'Nathalie Bose-Silver',jobTitle:'Catholic Spiritual Director',telephone:'+1-321-231-0058',email,areaServed:['Oviedo, Florida','Winter Park, Florida'],knowsLanguage:['English','Spanish'] };
---
<!doctype html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"/><title>Nathalie Bose-Silver | Catholic Spiritual Director</title><meta name="description" content="Compassionate Catholic spiritual direction in English and Spanish. Begin with a free 30-minute consultation."/><meta property="og:title" content="Nathalie Bose-Silver | Spiritual Direction"/><meta property="og:description" content="A prayerful space to notice grace and discern your path."/><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><meta property="og:image" content="/images/spiritual-journey/spiritual-journey-logo.jpeg"/><script is:inline type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}/></head>
<body id="top"><a class="skip" href="#main">Skip to content</a><Header/>
<main id="main">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-index" aria-hidden="true"><span>01</span><i></i><small>Welcome</small></div>
    <div class="hero-copy"><p class="kicker">Catholic spiritual direction · English & Spanish</p><h1>A quieter way to hear what your <em>heart</em> already knows.</h1><p class="hero-lead">Step away from the noise. Enter a confidential, prayerful conversation where you can notice God’s movement and meet your life with clarity, courage, and grace.</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="primary-link" href={consultationHref}>Free 30-minute conversation <span>↗</span></a><a class="text-link" href={phoneHref}>{phoneDisplay} <span>→</span></a></div></div>
    <div class="hero-visual"><div class="orbit orbit-one"></div><div class="orbit orbit-two"></div><img src="/images/spiritual-journey/spiritual-journey-logo.jpeg" width="1024" height="1024" alt="Spiritual Journey emblem featuring a winding path, butterflies, hands holding a flame, and a dove."/><p><span>✦</span>A sacred pause<br/>for your unfolding path</p></div>
    <a class="scroll-cue" href="#practice"><span>Scroll to explore</span><i>↓</i></a>
  </section>

  <section class="manifesto" id="practice"><div class="section-number">02 / The practice</div><div class="manifesto-title"><p>Spiritual direction is</p><h2>Not advice.<br/>Not therapy.<br/><em>Sacred attention.</em></h2><figure class="practice-image"><img src="/images/spiritual-journey/prayer-silhouette.jpeg" alt="Silhouette of a person praying against a warm sunset sky." loading="lazy"/><figcaption>A space to listen beyond the noise.</figcaption></figure></div><div class="manifesto-copy"><p>It is a conversation centered on your relationship with God—a place to slow down, reflect, pray, and become attentive to grace in ordinary life.</p><p>Nathalie does not diagnose or hand you answers. She accompanies you as you recognize the Divine within and around you, and discern the path that is already unfolding.</p><aside>“A spiritual director is one who helps another to recognize and follow the inspirations of grace.”</aside></div></section>

  <section class="path-section" id="journey"><div class="path-heading"><div><span class="section-number">03 / The journey</span><h2>Four movements.<br/>One unfolding path.</h2></div><p>Monthly, one-hour conversations shaped around your life—not a formula.</p></div><div class="path-layout"><div class="path-line" aria-hidden="true"><span class="path-progress"></span></div>{expectations.map(([icon,title,text],i)=><article class="path-step"><span class="step-count">0{i+1}</span><div class="step-icon"><Icon name={icon}/></div><div><h3>{title}</h3><p>{text}</p></div></article>)}</div></section>

  <section class="approach"><div class="approach-sticky"><span class="section-number">04 / The approach</span><h2>Held with care.<br/>Guided by grace.</h2><p>Every session is an invitation to pause and listen deeply to what is moving within your heart.</p></div><div class="approach-panels">{approach.map(([title,text],i)=><article><span>{String(i+1).padStart(2,'0')}</span><h3>{title}</h3><p>{text}</p></article>)}</div></section>

  <section class="profile" id="nathalie"><figure class="profile-mark profile-photo"><img src="/images/spiritual-journey/profile-pic.jpeg" alt="Portrait of Nathalie Bose-Silver smiling in an orange jacket." loading="lazy"/><figcaption>Compassionate presence · Prayerful listening</figcaption></figure><div class="profile-copy"><span class="section-number">05 / Your companion</span><h2>Meet Nathalie<br/>Bose-Silver.</h2><p class="profile-intro">A certified professional spiritual director rooted in the Catholic faith and open to the unique sacred story of every person.</p><div class="profile-columns"><p>Nathalie completed the Sacred Presence Program at San Pedro Center, a ministry of the Diocese of Orlando, and is a member of Spiritual Directors International.</p><p>Her experience includes adult and youth faith formation and founding a nonprofit rosary-making ministry supporting deeper devotion and prayer.</p></div><div class="credentials"><span>Certified Spiritual Director</span><span>English & Spanish</span><span>SDI Member</span></div></div></section>

  <section class="meeting"><div class="meeting-intro"><span class="section-number">06 / Where we meet</span><h2>Wherever you can<br/>be fully present.</h2></div><div class="meeting-options"><article><Icon name="video"/><span>01</span><h3>Zoom</h3><p>Meet face-to-face from a private, comfortable place of your choosing.</p></article><article><Icon name="phone"/><span>02</span><h3>Phone</h3><p>A simple and accessible way to connect from wherever you feel at ease.</p></article><article><Icon name="place"/><span>03</span><h3>In person</h3><p>By appointment in Oviedo or Winter Park, Florida.</p></article></div></section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact"><div class="contact-symbol" aria-hidden="true">✦</div><p>Begin with a complimentary conversation</p><h2>Perhaps your next step<br/>is simply to <em>begin.</em></h2><div class="contact-actions"><a href={consultationHref}>Email Nathalie <span>↗</span></a><a href={phoneHref}>Call {phoneDisplay}</a></div><div class="contact-meta"><span>{email}</span><span>English & Spanish</span><span>Zoom · Phone · In person</span></div></section>
</main>
<footer><div><strong>Nathalie Bose-Silver</strong><span>Catholic Spiritual Director</span></div><nav><a href="#practice">Practice</a><a href="#journey">Journey</a><a href="#nathalie">About</a><a href="#contact">Contact</a></nav><p>© {year} Nathalie Bose-Silver.<br/>Spiritual direction is not a substitute for counseling, psychotherapy, medical care, or emergency services.</p></footer>
<script>import '../scripts/animations';</script></body></html>
